{"word":"ἀξιόλογος","slug":"ἀξιόλογος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀξιόλογος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>λέγω</el>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>worthy of mention, noteworthy</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <el>πόλεμος ἀξιολογώτατος</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>:— <a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a> <el>-γως</el>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>of persons, <i>of note, important</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}